  <entry>
    <title>在2020年捡一台iPhone4</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/2020/10/17/%E5%9C%A82020%E5%B9%B4%E6%8D%A1%E4%B8%80%E5%8F%B0iPhone4/"/>
    <id>http://example.com/2020/10/17/%E5%9C%A82020%E5%B9%B4%E6%8D%A1%E4%B8%80%E5%8F%B0iPhone4/</id>
    <published>2020-10-17T00:00:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-07-31T01:22:12.296Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="捡垃圾"><a href="#捡垃圾" class="headerlink" title="捡垃圾"></a>捡垃圾</h1><p>下面这是我从同学手里捡来的写号机 <br/></p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sanksu/Blog-Old@master/image/_posts/iPhone4_2.jpg" alt="战痕累累的iPhone4_背面与侧面"><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sanksu/Blog-Old@master/image/_posts/iPhone4_3.jpg" alt="战痕累累的iPhone4_背面与侧面_2"><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sanksu/Blog-Old@master/image/_posts/iPhone4_4.jpg" alt="战痕累累的iPhone4_正面"></p><h2 id="经典的锁屏界面"><a href="#经典的锁屏界面" class="headerlink" title="经典的锁屏界面"></a>经典的锁屏界面</h2><p>本来拿来想降到IOS6的，结果发现是iPhone3,3 orz<br/></p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sanksu/Blog-Old@master/image/_posts/IOS6-unlock.jpg" alt="网上找的"></p><h1 id="如今"><a href="#如今" class="headerlink" title="如今"></a>如今</h1><p>IOS7已经没有多少能用的应用了 <br/><br>旧版本的bilibili能打开，但不能登录账号，由于屏幕小，虽然是流畅分辨率，清晰的却还可以 <br/><br>没有什么游戏可以玩。但是我还是找到了的安装包无尽之剑，即使现在被下架了，( ͡° ͜ʖ ͡°) <br/></p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sanksu/Blog-Old@master/image/_posts/Infinity-Blade.jpg" alt="贴吧找的"></p>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">一代经典——iPhone4</summary>
    
    
    
